_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9785168372553299, \"rank\": 0.021954817201296793, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Decorated AmericanswimmerCaeleb Dressel\", \"from\": 223, \"to\": 262}, {\"ngram\": \"tears\", \"from\": 277, \"to\": 282}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday atthe Summer Games\", \"from\": 286, \"to\": 311}, {\"ngram\": \"Parisas\", \"from\": 315, \"to\": 322}, {\"ngram\": \"chances\", \"from\": 333, \"to\": 340}, {\"ngram\": \"his Olympic titles\", \"from\": 358, \"to\": 376}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shortly after a sixth-place showing in the 50-meter freestyle, he failed to reach the final in the 100 butterfly.\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 522, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 50-meter freestyle\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 470}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100 butterfly\", \"from\": 504, \"to\": 521}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stream NBC 5 for free, 24/7, wherever you are.\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 570, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Stream\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 530}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Obviously it's not my best work,\\\" Dressel said.\", \"from\": 572, \"to\": 620, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my best work\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 604}, {\"ngram\": \"Dressel\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 614}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had a lot of fun though, I can honestly say that.\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 673, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 628, \"to\": 633}, {\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 640}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has not been my best week, I do not think I need to shy away from that, but the racing's been really fun here.\\\"\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 788, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my best week\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 702}, {\"ngram\": \"the racing\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 763}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bouncing along moments before his freestyle race, Dressel made his way onto the pool deck when his name was introduced looking confident as ever.\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 935, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"moments\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 812}, {\"ngram\": \"his freestyle race\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 838}, {\"ngram\": \"Dressel\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 847}, {\"ngram\": \"his way\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 860}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool deck\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 879}, {\"ngram\": \"his name\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 893}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He raised his arms and side-shuffled to reach his spot in Lane 2.\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 1001, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his arms\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 954}, {\"ngram\": \"his spot\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 990}, {\"ngram\": \"Lane\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 998}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dressel set Olympic records while winning both the 50 free and 100 fly - the latter also a world record - among his five golds at the Tokyo Games, but touched the wall in 21.61 for sixth in the free Thursday.\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1211, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dressel\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1010}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic records\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1030}, {\"ngram\": \"his five golds\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1129}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Games\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1148}, {\"ngram\": \"the wall\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1170}, {\"ngram\": \"the free Thursday\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1210}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His fly semifinal was a shocking 13th-fastest.\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1258, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His fly semifinal\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1229}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old Dressel has been cheered on by wife Meghan and their five-month-old son, August, sporting oversized protective headphones in the deafening noise of La Defense Aren